blog.title: Pokemon Biology and Behavior
blog.description:
Hello! My name is Breeze, and I'm a Pokemon Breeder. I make a living out of raising, breeding, and helping pokemon of all sorts. I've learned a lot through my work and am hoping to share my findings, so feel free to ask about any pokemon you see fit. Except legendaries. I don't really get to interact with those often.

((Icon by yumiponypup))

title: Duskull Line Fact 1
body: The Duskull line as actually some of the kindest and most loyal ghost-types out there. A Dusknoir has makes for a fantastic babysitter as it won’t let any living or dead threat get near your child, and the other two can do well in guarding as well.

This movie will show 7 times just so you won’t miss the stream, and watch it in the most convenient time depending on your schedule at 10:15am | 1pm | 4pm | 7pm | 10pm | 1am | 4am (PDT, UTC−07:00)

Watching with Twitch chat could be the best (or worst) experience you’ll ever have! But if you want a more comfy chat experience, feel free to talk/chat about the marathon in my Pokémon Discord server PokéTōku —> Invite link here :)

blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary:
Sherbesaur Bulbasaur and Sherbet fusion Nutritional Information: Sugar Type Ability: Sherbet Power - 

Powers up moves of the...
caption:
Sherbesaur

Bulbasaur and Sherbet fusion

Nutritional Information:

Sugar Type

Ability: Sherbet Power -  Powers up moves of the same type as the Pokefood

Signature Move: Fizzplosion - The user shoots a fizzy ball at the opponent which explodes violently. Power 130, Accuracy 95. Requires a turn of recharge. 

The Sugary Fizz Pokefood

Sherbesaur releases its sherbet powder into the air which get people excited.  Although Sherbesaur is mainly found in yellow, it can come in a variety of different colours.  

A bulbasaur and sherbet fusion for day 7 of the Halloween event suggested by @ohnonotthemagain. I don’t know if Americans have the sweets that I’ve used here but I made this boy out of sherbet lemons, pink sherbet sweets and flying saucers.
